dct_title_s: Dilli ke nikatavarti kshetra ka rekhacitra, lagabhaga 1807 = Sketch of the environs of Delhi, circa 1807
dct_description_sm: Survey of India. Alternate title [from original version]: Sketch of the environs of Delhi. Relief shown by hachuresIn upper left margin. "Reproduced from a hand drawn original of 1807." Map is a facsimile.
